ActJudges Act (Removal Allowance) Order
PrecisOrder prescribing additional periods during which certain RELOCATION EXPENSES may be reimbursed to The Hon. KELLY A. GORMAN, who was required to relocate to the City of London in Ontario, following his appointment as a Judge of the Superior Court of Justice of Ontario on April 11, 2008 .
